snippet.title: Sega Rally 2 - [Dreamcast] - Trailer
snippet.description:
Title: Sega Rally 2
Publisher: Sega
Developer: AM2
Genre: Driving
Release Date: October 14, 1999
Description: The ultimate rally racer. Choose from more than 20 cars,
customize it from wheels to transmission, and race across 18 different
tracks in several play modes. Also one of the first Dreamcast games to
support network play. Sprawdź mój Twitch: www.twitch.tv/cosmaty
